@startuml Redux_Cart_Init
title Redux Cart - Store Initialization & Hydration

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam ParticipantPadding 18
skinparam BoxPadding 10

box "Redux Store" #E8F6F3
participant "cartStore" as Store
participant "rootReducer\n(combineReducers)" as RootReducer
participant "cartReducer" as CartReducer
end box

box "Persistence" #FCF3CF
participant "cartStorage" as Storage
end box

autonumber 1

Store -> Storage : readStoredCartRows()
Storage --> Store : CartRow[]

Store -> Store : build preloadedState\n{ cart: { items: [...] } }

Store -> RootReducer : create store with preloadedState
RootReducer -> CartReducer : initialize cart slice
CartReducer --> RootReducer : CartState
RootReducer --> Store : store ready

note over Store
combineReducers includes:
- cart: cartReducer
- toast: toastReducer
end note

Store -> Store : subscribe()
Store -> Storage : on every state change,\nwriteStoredCartRows(state.cart.items)

@enduml